---
import Blockquote from "../components/Blockquote.astro";
---

<div class="columns" id="introduction">
  <div class="left">
    <hgroup>
      <h2>Slowbuilt: Workshop</h2>
      <p class="lead">Growth, Without Panic</p>
      <hr />
      <p class="small">A companion workshop series for the Slowbuilt book.</p>
    </hgroup>
  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <h3>What is it?</h3>
    <p>
      Slowbuilt is a three-session workshop series designed to help students,
      educators, and school communities rethink how growth, progress, and
      potential are understood. Rather than motivating through pressure or
      addressing disengagement with compliance-based fixes, Slowbuilt helps
      participants reinterpret progress accurately, recognize misalignment
      instead of failure, and regain agency without urgency.
    </p>
    <p>
      The workshop is experiential, reflective, and psychologically safe. It
      does not use diagnostic language, require public sharing, or promote
      one-size-fits-all solutions.
    </p>

    <h3>How it works</h3>
    <p>
      The series consists of three 75–90 minute sessions, each built around an
      anchor activity that participants experience before any explanation or
      instruction.
    </p>

    <ul class="links">
      <li>
        <a class="yellow" href="mailto:mark@markgodi.com"
          >Contact me for more information</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .columns {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-block: 0 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 120ch) {
    .columns {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .columns > div {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .left {
    max-width: 35rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .left {
      max-width: 25rem;
    }
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block: 2rem 1.25rem;
  }

  hgroup p {
    font-family: "EB Garamond", serif;
    /* font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.25rem); */
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  p.lead {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-family: "EB Garamond", serif;
  }

  p.small {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-top: 0;
    font-family: "EB Garamond", serif;
  }

  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 2px solid #ebc975;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  .links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links {
      flex-direction: row;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  .links a {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0.02rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 500;
    min-width: 20rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    margin-block: auto;
    color: #244057;
    background-color: #ebc975;
  }
  @media (min-width: 80ch) {
    .links a {
      padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
      min-width: 15rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }

  .links a:hover {
    background-color: #244057;
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
</style>
